{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876433962,"sessionID":"ses_28584361cffeH5b0m4JrSVKROR","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7be399001nIByjGw5JSqSTO","messageID":"msg_d7a7bdc61001jg7ByTYOttmJcv","sessionID":"ses_28584361cffeH5b0m4JrSVKROR","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d650e29d58dc452db22e03fe","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** docker\n4: > **Language:** Dockerfile\n5: > **Size:** S\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-032/design.md`, `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n8: > **Dependency:** None (greenfield — `docker/` directory does not exist yet)\n9: \n10: ---\n11: \n12: ## T-001: 创建 docker/ 目录与 .dockerignore\n13: \n14: - [ ] T-001.01 创建 `docker/` 目录\n15: - [ ] T-001.02 创建 `docker/.dockerignore`，排除 `.git`、`.gitignore`、`test/`、`testing/`、`sdk-python/`、`docs/`、`coverage.out`、`.pytest_cache/`、`.coverage`、`*.md`（保留 `!README.md`）\n16: \n17: **验收**: `ls docker/.dockerignore` 文件存在；`grep -c \"\\.git\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 1；`grep -c \"test/\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 1\n18: \n19: ---\n20: \n21: ## T-002: Workload Manager Dockerfile (docker/Dockerfile)\n22: \n23: - [ ] T-002.01 Stage 1 (builder): `FROM golang:1.25-alpine AS builder`，设置 `WORKDIR /workspace`\n24: - [ ] T-002.02 Builder: `COPY go.mod go.sum ./` 后 `RUN go mod download`（层缓存优化）\n25: - [ ] T-002.03 Builder: `COPY cmd/ cmd/` 和 `COPY pkg/ pkg/`\n26: - [ ] T-002.04 Builder: `RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o /workloadmanager ./cmd/workloadmanager`\n27: - [ ] T-002.05 Stage 2 (runtime): `FROM alpine:3.19`，`RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates`\n28: - [ ] T-002.06 Runtime: `WORKDIR /app`，`COPY --from=builder /workloadmanager /app/workloadmanager`\n29: - [ ] T-002.07 Runtime: `RUN adduser -D -u 1000 apiserver`，`USER apiserver`\n30: - [ ] T-002.08 Runtime: `EXPOSE 8080`，`ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/workloadmanager\"]`，`CMD [\"--port=8080\"]`\n31: \n32: **验收**: `grep -c \"FROM golang:1.25-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile` → 1；`grep -c \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile` → 1；`grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile` 有输出；`grep \"adduser.*1000 apiserver\" docker/Dockerfile` 有输出；`grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile` 有输出；`grep 'ENTRYPOINT' docker/Dockerfile` 含 `/app/workloadmanager`\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## T-003: Router Dockerfile (docker/Dockerfile.router)\n37: \n38: - [ ] T-003.01 Stage 1 (builder): `FROM golang:1.25-alpine AS builder`，设置 `WORKDIR /workspace`\n39: - [ ] T-003.02 Builder: `COPY go.mod go.sum ./` 后 `RUN go mod download`\n40: - [ ] T-003.03 Builder: `COPY cmd/ cmd/`、`COPY pkg/ pkg/`、`COPY client-go/ client-go/`\n41: - [ ] T-003.04 Builder: `RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o /agentcube-router ./cmd/router`\n42: - [ ] T-003.05 Stage 2 (runtime): `FROM alpine:3.19`，`RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates`\n43: - [ ] T-003.06 Runtime: `WORKDIR /app`，`COPY --from=builder /agentcube-router /app/agentcube-router`\n44: - [ ] T-003.07 Runtime: `RUN adduser -D -u 1000 router`，`USER router`\n45: - [ ] T-003.08 Runtime: `EXPOSE 8080`，`ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/agentcube-router\"]`，`CMD [\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]`\n46: \n47: **验收**: `grep -c \"FROM golang:1.25-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile.router` → 1；`grep -c \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile.router` → 1；`grep \"COPY client-go/\" docker/Dockerfile.router` 有输出；`grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile.router` 有输出；`grep \"adduser.*1000 router\" docker/Dockerfile.router` 有输出；`grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile.router` 有输出；`grep 'ENTRYPOINT' docker/Dockerfile.router` 含 `/app/agentcube-router`\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## T-004: PicoD Dockerfile (docker/Dockerfile.picod)\n52: \n53: - [ ] T-004.01 Stage 1 (builder): `FROM golang:1.25-alpine AS builder`，设置 `WORKDIR /workspace`\n54: - [ ] T-004.02 Builder: `COPY go.mod go.sum ./` 后 `RUN go mod download`\n55: - [ ] T-004.03 Builder: `COPY cmd/ cmd/`、`COPY pkg/ pkg/`\n56: - [ ] T-004.04 Builder: `RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o /picod ./cmd/picod`\n57: - [ ] T-004.05 Stage 2 (runtime): `FROM alpine:3.19`，`RUN apk add --no-cache python3`\n58: - [ ] T-004.06 Runtime: `WORKDIR /app`，`COPY --from=builder /picod /app/picod`\n59: - [ ] T-004.07 Runtime: `RUN adduser -D -u 1000 picod`，`USER picod`\n60: - [ ] T-004.08 Runtime: `ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/picod\"]`（无 EXPOSE，无 CMD）\n61: \n62: **验收**: `grep -c \"FROM golang:1.25-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` → 1；`grep -c \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` → 1；`grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` 有输出；`grep \"apk add.*python3\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` 有输出；`grep \"adduser.*1000 picod\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` 有输出；`grep \"EXPOSE\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` 无输出；`grep 'ENTRYPOINT' docker/Dockerfile.picod` 含 `/app/picod`\n63: \n64: ---\n65: \n66: ## T-005: 三镜像构建验证\n67: \n68: - [ ] T-005.01 `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t wm:test .` 成功（退出码 0）\n69: - [ ] T-005.02 `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t router:test .` 成功（退出码 0）\n70: - [ ] T-005.03 `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t picod:test .` 成功（退出码 0）\n71: \n72: **验收**: 三条 `docker build` 命令均退出码 0；`docker image ls | grep -E \"wm:test|router:test|picod:test\"` 显示三个镜像\n73: \n74: ---\n75: \n76: ## T-006: 镜像内容静态验证\n77: \n78: - [ ] T-006.01 三个镜像均不包含 Go 工具链：`docker run --rm <image> which go` 返回非 0\n79: - [ ] T-006.02 WM 镜像含二进制：`docker run --rm wm:test ls -la /app/workloadmanager` 有输出\n80: - [ ] T-006.03 Router 镜像含二进制：`docker run --rm router:test ls -la /app/agentcube-router` 有输出\n81: - [ ] T-006.04 PicoD 镜像含二进制：`docker run --rm picod:test ls -la /app/picod` 有输出\n82: - [ ] T-006.05 PicoD 镜像含 python3：`docker run --rm picod:test which python3` 有输出\n83: - [ ] T-006.06 WM/Router 镜像含 ca-certificates：`docker run --rm wm:test ls /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt` 有输出\n84: \n85: **验收**: T-006.01 三个镜像 `which go` 均失败；T-006.02~006.04 二进制文件均存在；T-006.05 `which python3` 在 picod 镜像中返回路径；T-006.06 ca-certificates 文件存在于 WM/Router 镜像\n86: \n87: ---\n88: \n89: ## T-007: 非 root 用户验证\n90: \n91: - [ ] T-007.01 WM 镜像运行 UID = 1000：`docker run --rm wm:test id -u` 输出 `1000`\n92: - [ ] T-007.02 Router 镜像运行 UID = 1000：`docker run --rm router:test id -u` 输出 `1000`\n93: - [ ] T-007.03 PicoD 镜像运行 UID = 1000：`docker run --rm picod:test id -u` 输出 `1000`\n94: \n95: **验收**: 三条 `docker run --rm <image> id -u` 均输出 `1000`\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ## T-008: 端口暴露与入口点验证\n100: \n101: - [ ] T-008.01 WM 镜像 ExposedPorts 含 8080：`docker inspect wm:test --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}'` 含 `\"8080/tcp\"`\n102: - [ ] T-008.02 Router 镜像 ExposedPorts 含 8080：`docker inspect router:test --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}'` 含 `\"8080/tcp\"`\n103: - [ ] T-008.03 PicoD 镜像无 ExposedPorts：`docker inspect picod:test --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}'` 输出 `null` 或 `{}`\n104: - [ ] T-008.04 WM 镜像 Entrypoint 为 `/app/workloadmanager`：`docker inspect wm:test --format='{{json .Config.Entrypoint}}'` 含 `/app/workloadmanager`\n105: - [ ] T-008.05 Router 镜像 Entrypoint 为 `/app/agentcube-router`：`docker inspect router:test --format='{{json .Config.Entrypoint}}'` 含 `/app/agentcube-router`\n106: - [ ] T-008.06 PicoD 镜像 Entrypoint 为 `/app/picod`：`docker inspect picod:test --format='{{json .Config.Entrypoint}}'` 含 `/app/picod`\n107: \n108: **验收**: 六个 `docker inspect` 命令输出均符合预期\n109: \n110: ---\n111: \n112: ## T-009: 镜像大小验证\n113: \n114: - [ ] T-009.01 WM 镜像大小 < 50 MB\n115: - [ ] T-009.02 Router 镜像大小 < 50 MB\n116: - [ ] T-009.03 PicoD 镜像大小 < 100 MB（含 python3）\n117: \n118: **验收**: `docker image inspect wm:test --format='{{.Size}}'` 输出 < 52428800；`docker image inspect router:test --format='{{.Size}}'` 输出 < 52428800；`docker image inspect picod:test --format='{{.Size}}'` 输出 < 104857600\n119: \n120: ---\n121: \n122: ## T-010: 目录结构最终验证\n123: \n124: - [ ] T-010.01 `docker/` 目录包含 `Dockerfile`、`Dockerfile.router`、`Dockerfile.picod`、`.dockerignore` 四个文件\n125: - [ ] T-010.02 三个 Dockerfile 均使用两阶段构建（`FROM ... AS builder` + `FROM alpine:3.19`）\n126: - [ ] T-010.03 三个 Dockerfile 均包含 `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` 编译标志\n127: - [ ] T-010.04 三个 Dockerfile 均包含 `GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH}` 跨平台支持\n128: \n129: **验收**: `ls docker/` 输出四个文件；`grep -l \"FROM.*AS builder\" docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配三个文件；`grep -l 'ldflags=\"-s -w\"' docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配三个文件；`grep -l \"GOOS=\\${TARGETOS}\" docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配三个文件\n130: \n131: ---\n132: \n133: ## Dependency Graph\n134: \n135: ```\n136: T-001 (docker/ + .dockerignore) ──┬── T-002 (WM Dockerfile) ──┐\n137:                                    ├── T-003 (Router Dockerfile)├── T-005 (build all 3)\n138:                                    └── T-004 (PicoD Dockerfile) ┤\n139:                                                               ├── T-006 (content verify)\n140:                                                               ├── T-007 (non-root verify)\n141:                                                               ├── T-008 (ports/entrypoint)\n142:                                                               ├── T-009 (size verify)\n143:                                                               └── T-010 (structure verify)\n144: ```\n145: \n146: ## Parallelizable Groups\n147: \n148: | Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n149: |-------|-------|---------------|\n150: | G1 | T-001 (docker/ + .dockerignore) | None |\n151: | G2 | T-002 (WM), T-003 (Router), T-004 (PicoD) | G1 |\n152: | G3 | T-005 (build all 3) | G2 |\n153: | G4 | T-006 (content), T-007 (non-root), T-008 (ports), T-009 (size), T-010 (structure) | G3 |\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ## Acceptance Criteria\n158: \n159: | # | Criterion | Command |\n160: |---|-----------|---------|\n161: | AC1 | `docker/` 目录存在且含 4 个文件 | `ls docker/` 输出 `Dockerfile Dockerfile.router Dockerfile.picod .dockerignore` |\n162: | AC2 | .dockerignore 排除 `.git`、`test/`、`docs/` | `grep -c \"\\.git\\|test/\\|docs/\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 3 |\n163: | AC3 | WM Dockerfile 使用 golang:1.25-alpine + alpine:3.19 | `grep \"FROM golang:1.25-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile` && `grep \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile` |\n164: | AC4 | WM Dockerfile 编译 ./cmd/workloadmanager，CGO_ENABLED=0 | `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0.*workloadmanager\" docker/Dockerfile` |\n165: | AC5 | WM Dockerfile 创建 apiserver (UID 1000)，EXPOSE 8080 | `grep \"adduser.*1000 apiserver\" docker/Dockerfile` && `grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile` |\n166: | AC6 | Router Dockerfile 额外 COPY client-go/ | `grep \"COPY client-go/\" docker/Dockerfile.router` |\n167: | AC7 | Router Dockerfile 创建 router (UID 1000)，EXPOSE 8080 | `grep \"adduser.*1000 router\" docker/Dockerfile.router` && `grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile.router` |\n168: | AC8 | PicoD Dockerfile 安装 python3，无 EXPOSE | `grep \"apk add.*python3\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` && `! grep \"EXPOSE\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` |\n169: | AC9 | PicoD Dockerfile 创建 picod (UID 1000) | `grep \"adduser.*1000 picod\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` |\n170: | AC10 | 三镜像构建成功 | `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t wm:test .` && `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t router:test .` && `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t picod:test .` 均退出码 0 |\n171: | AC11 | 三镜像无 Go 工具链 | `docker run --rm wm:test which go \\|\\| true` 无输出；Router/PicoD 同理 |\n172: | AC12 | 三镜像运行时 UID = 1000 | `docker run --rm wm:test id -u` → 1000；Router/PicoD 同理 |\n173: | AC13 | WM/Router EXPOSE 8080，PicoD 无 | `docker inspect wm:test --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}'` 含 8080；PicoD 为 null |\n174: | AC14 | WM 镜像 < 50MB，Router < 50MB，PicoD < 100MB | `docker image inspect <image> --format='{{.Size}}'` 分别验证 |\n175: | AC15 | 三 Dockerfile 均含 -ldflags=\"-s -w\" | `grep -l 'ldflags=\"-s -w\"' docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配 3 个文件 |\n176: | AC16 | 三 Dockerfile 均含跨平台构建支持 | `grep -l 'GOOS=\\${TARGETOS}' docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配 3 个文件 |\n\n(End of file - total 176 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** docker\n> **Language:** Dockerfile\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-032/design.md`, `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n> **Dependency:** None (greenfield — `docker/` directory does not exist yet)\n\n---\n\n## T-001: 创建 docker/ 目录与 .dockerignore\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 创建 `docker/` 目录\n- [ ] T-001.02 创建 `docker/.dockerignore`，排除 `.git`、`.gitignore`、`test/`、`testing/`、`sdk-python/`、`docs/`、`coverage.out`、`.pytest_cache/`、`.coverage`、`*.md`（保留 `!README.md`）\n\n**验收**: `ls docker/.dockerignore` 文件存在；`grep -c \"\\.git\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 1；`grep -c \"test/\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 1\n\n---\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775876433944,"end":1775876433960}}}}
