{"type":"text","timestamp":1775876475626,"sessionID":"ses_28584361cffeH5b0m4JrSVKROR","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7c5eb5001fKgnq3hWTL6ahw","messageID":"msg_d7a7c21d6001w5hucqpPoESw6V","sessionID":"ses_28584361cffeH5b0m4JrSVKROR","type":"text","text":"## AR-032 Archive Summary\n\n### Completed\n\n**Artifacts created (4 files in `docker/`):**\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `docker/.dockerignore` | Excludes `.git`, `test/`, `testing/`, `sdk-python/`, `docs/`, coverage artifacts, `*.md` (keeps `!README.md`) |\n| `docker/Dockerfile` | Workload Manager — golang:1.25-alpine → alpine:3.19, `CGO_ENABLED=0`, non-root `apiserver` (UID 1000), EXPOSE 8080 |\n| `docker/Dockerfile.router` | Router — same pattern + `COPY client-go/`, non-root `router` (UID 1000), EXPOSE 8080, `--debug` CMD |\n| `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | PicoD — same pattern + `apk add python3`, non-root `picod` (UID 1000), no EXPOSE |\n\n**All three Dockerfiles include:**\n- BuildKit cache mounts (`--mount=type=cache`) for `/go/pkg/mod` and `/root/.cache/go-build`\n- `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` stripping\n- `GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH}` cross-platform support\n- Layer caching optimization (`go.mod`/`go.sum` copied before source)\n\n### Deferred (not implemented in this AR)\n\n| Item | Type | Notes |\n|------|------|-------|\n| **T-005 through T-010** (all verification tasks) | Runtime validation | Docker build, image content, non-root UID, ports/entrypoint, size, and structure verification — all tasks remain unchecked |\n| **AgentD Dockerfile** | Follow-up AR | `cmd/agentd` needs its own Dockerfile following the same pattern |\n| **Image digest pinning** | Follow-up | Replace `alpine:3.19` / `golang:1.25-alpine` with digest-pinned versions for production |\n| **Multi-arch build (buildx)** | Follow-up | Makefile `docker-buildx` target needs adaptation to new Dockerfile paths |\n| **Image push (CI/CD)** | Follow-up | CI pipeline to build and push to `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/` |\n| **Security scanning** | Follow-up | Trivy/Grype CVE scanning integration |\n| **Further image size optimization** | Follow-up | Evaluate `distroless` or `scratch` as runtime base |\n| **Helm chart image reference update** | Follow-up | `values.yaml` `image.repository` needs to point to correct registry paths |","time":{"start":1775876475622,"end":1775876475622}}}
